---
/**
 * Origin-story section, explains the AWL split from All Webbed Up.
 * Sits between home-entity (one-line tech-arm strapline) and TrustedBy
 * (client logos). Establishes brand context before social proof.
 *
 * Layout: two side-by-side brand cards joined by a vertical accent rule
 * + a centered "+" marker. Below: a single narrative paragraph.
 */
---

<section class="story-section" id="our-story" aria-labelledby="our-story-heading">
  <div class="story-inner">
    <div class="story-header reveal">
      <span class="story-eyebrow">Our story</span>
      <h2 id="our-story-heading" class="story-heading">
        Born from years of building.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="story-grid reveal">
      <!-- Parent brand -->
      <article class="story-card story-card--parent">
        <div class="story-card__mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="story-card__letter">AWU</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story-card__name">All Webbed Up</h3>
        <p class="story-card__role">Marketing &amp; growth</p>
        <p class="story-card__body">
          Brands, campaigns, content and storytelling for Australian
          businesses. The parent company, still going.
        </p>
        <a class="story-card__link" href="https://allwebbedup.com.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          allwebbedup.com.au
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7"/><path d="M8 7h9v9"/></svg>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="story-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="story-connector__rule"></span>
        <span class="story-connector__plus">+</span>
        <span class="story-connector__rule"></span>
      </div>

      <!-- This brand -->
      <article class="story-card story-card--labs">
        <div class="story-card__mark story-card__mark--accent" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="story-card__letter">AWL</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story-card__name">All Webbed Labs</h3>
        <p class="story-card__role">Technology &amp; AI</p>
        <p class="story-card__body">
          Custom software, autonomous AI agents, automation and Web3 for
          the same calibre of clients. The tech arm.
        </p>
        <span class="story-card__here">
          <span class="story-card__pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          You're here
        </span>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="story-narrative reveal stagger-1">
      After dozens of products built inside All Webbed Up, we knew the tech
      deserved its own room. So we branched off. <strong>All Webbed Labs</strong>
      now focuses purely on software, AI and automation; <strong>All Webbed Up</strong>
      continues as the marketing arm. Same team, two specialised crafts.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .story-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(13,147,115,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 50% 100%, rgba(13,147,115,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .story-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .story-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .story-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: #0d9373;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .story-eyebrow::before,
  .story-eyebrow::after {
    content: '';
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.55);
  }

  .story-heading {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 24, 23, 0.6) 0%, rgba(10, 14, 13, 0.6) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2.25rem 2rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .story-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.45);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -30px rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.35);
  }
  .story-card--labs {
    border-color: rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.15) inset;
  }

  .story-card__mark {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .story-card__mark--accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9373 0%, #0a6f57 100%);
    border-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -10px rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.6);
  }
  .story-card__letter {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .story-card__name {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .story-card__role {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0d9373;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
  }
  .story-card__body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(205, 224, 218, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .story-card__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0d9373;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.35);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    width: max-content;
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .story-card__link:hover {
    color: #14b58e;
    border-color: #14b58e;
  }

  .story-card__here {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(205, 224, 218, 0.85);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    width: max-content;
  }
  .story-card__pulse {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #0d9373;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.7);
    animation: story-pulse 1.8s ease-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes story-pulse {
    0%   { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.65); }
    70%  { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(13, 147, 115, 0); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(13, 147, 115, 0); }
  }

  /* Connector between the two cards */
  .story-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.6);
  }
  .story-connector__rule {
    width: 1px;
    flex: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.4), transparent);
    min-height: 40px;
  }
  .story-connector__plus {
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #0d9373;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .story-narrative {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(205, 224, 218, 0.88);
  }
  .story-narrative strong {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Tablet, collapse connector to horizontal */
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .story-connector {
      flex-direction: row;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    .story-connector__rule {
      width: auto;
      height: 1px;
      min-height: 0;
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(13, 147, 115, 0.4), transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .story-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
    .story-inner { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
    .story-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .story-card { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; }
    .story-narrative { font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  }
</style>
